{"id":284,"parent_id":277,"book_id":1,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":284,"title":"2 Samuel 7","subtitle":"","short_title":"2 Sam.","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/7","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 7"],[".studySummary",["i","David offers to build a house for the Lord—The Lord, through Nathan, says He has not asked David to do so—The Lord will establish David’s house and kingdom forever—David offers a prayer of thanksgiving."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/7.1","order":"02.11.007.22760"},["b","1"],"And it came to pass, when the king sat in his house, and the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"had given him",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"rest"],"round about from all his enemies;"],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/7.2","order":"02.11.007.22761"},["b","2"],"That the king said unto Nathan the prophet, See now, I dwell in an house of cedar, but the ark of God dwelleth within",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"curtains"],"."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/7.3","order":"02.11.007.22762"},["b","3"],"And Nathan said to the king, Go, do all that",["i","is"],"in thine",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"heart"],"; for the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],["i","is"],"with thee."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/7.4","order":"02.11.007.22763"},["b","4"],"¶And it came to pass that night, that the word of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"came unto",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"Nathan"],", saying,"],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/7.5","order":"02.11.007.22764"},["b","5"],"Go and tell my servant David, Thus saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", Shalt thou build me an",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"house"],"for me to dwell in?"],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/7.6","order":"02.11.007.22765"},["b","6"],"Whereas I have not dwelt in",["i","any"],"house since the time that I brought up the children of Israel out of Egypt, even to this day, but have walked in a tent and in a tabernacle."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/7.7","order":"02.11.007.22766"},["b","7"],"In all",["i","the places"],"wherein I have walked with all the children of Israel spake I a word with any of the tribes of Israel, whom I commanded to feed my people Israel, saying, Why build ye not me an",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"house"],"of cedar?"],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/7.8","order":"02.11.007.22767"},["b","8"],"Now therefore so shalt thou say unto my servant David, Thus saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"of hosts, I took thee from the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"sheepcote"],", from following the sheep, to be ruler over my people, over Israel:"],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/7.9","order":"02.11.007.22768"},["b","9"],"And I was with thee whithersoever thou wentest, and have cut off all thine enemies out of thy sight, and have made thee a great name, like unto the name of the great",["i","men"],"that",["i","are"],"in the earth."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/7.10","order":"02.11.007.22769"},["b","10"],"Moreover I will appoint a place for my people Israel, and will plant them, that they may dwell in a place of their own, and move no more; neither shall the children of wickedness afflict them any more, as beforetime,"],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/7.11","order":"02.11.007.22770"},["b","11"],"And as since the time that I commanded",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"judges"],["i","to be"],"over my people Israel, and have caused thee to",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_11b"},"rest"],"from all thine enemies. Also the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"telleth thee that he will make thee an",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_11c"},"house"],"."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/7.12","order":"02.11.007.22771"},["b","12"],"¶And when thy days be fulfilled, and thou shalt sleep with thy fathers, I will set up thy",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_12a"},"seed"],"after thee, which shall proceed out of thy bowels, and I will establish his kingdom."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/7.13","order":"02.11.007.22772"},["b","13"],"He shall",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"build"],"an house for my name, and I will",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_13b"},"stablish"],"the throne of his kingdom for ever."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/7.14","order":"02.11.007.22773"},["b","14"],"I will be his",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"father"],", and he shall be my",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_14b"},"son"],". If he commit iniquity, I will",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_14c"},"chasten"],"him with the rod of men, and with the stripes of the children of men:"],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/7.15","order":"02.11.007.22774"},["b","15"],"But my mercy shall not depart away from him, as I took",["i","it"],"from Saul, whom I put away before thee."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/7.16","order":"02.11.007.22775"},["b","16"],"And thine",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_16a"},"house"],"and thy kingdom shall be established for ever before thee: thy",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_16b"},"throne"],"shall be established for ever."],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/7.17","order":"02.11.007.22776"},["b","17"],"According to all these words, and according to all this vision, so did Nathan speak unto David."],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/7.18","order":"02.11.007.22777"},["b","18"],"¶Then went king David in, and sat before the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", and he said, Who",["i","am"],"I, O Lord",["span.smallCaps","God"],"? and what",["i","is"],"my house, that thou hast brought me hitherto?"],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/7.19","order":"02.11.007.22778"},["b","19"],"And this was yet a small thing in thy sight, O Lord",["span.smallCaps","God"],"; but thou hast spoken also of thy servant’s house for a great while to come. And",["i","is"],"this the manner of man, O Lord",["span.smallCaps","God"],"?"],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/7.20","order":"02.11.007.22779"},["b","20"],"And what can David say more unto thee? for thou, Lord",["span.smallCaps","God"],",",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_20a"},"knowest"],"thy servant."],["div",{"id":"21","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/7.21","order":"02.11.007.22780"},["b","21"],"For thy word’s sake, and according to thine own heart, hast thou done all these",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_21a"},"great things"],", to make thy servant know",["i","them."]],["div",{"id":"22","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/7.22","order":"02.11.007.22781"},["b","22"],"Wherefore thou art great, O",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"God: for",["i","there is"],"none",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_22a"},"like"],"thee, neither",["i","is there any"],"God beside thee, according to all that we have heard with our ears."],["div",{"id":"23","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/7.23","order":"02.11.007.22782"},["b","23"],"And what one",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_23a"},"nation"],"in the earth",["i","is"],"like thy people,",["i","even"],"like Israel, whom God went to redeem for a people to himself, and to make him a name, and to do for you great things and terrible, for thy land, before thy people, which thou redeemedst to thee from Egypt,",["i","from"],"the nations and their gods?"],["div",{"id":"24","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/7.24","order":"02.11.007.22783"},["b","24"],"For thou hast",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_24a"},"confirmed"],"to thyself thy people",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_24b"},"Israel"],["i","to be"],"a people unto thee for ever: and thou,",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", art become their God."],["div",{"id":"25","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/7.25","order":"02.11.007.22784"},["b","25"],"And now, O",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"God, the word that thou hast spoken concerning thy servant, and concerning his house,",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_25a"},"establish"],["i","it"],"for ever, and do as thou hast said."],["div",{"id":"26","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/7.26","order":"02.11.007.22785"},["b","26"],"And let thy name be magnified for ever, saying, The",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"of hosts",["i","is"],"the God over Israel: and let the house of thy servant David be established before thee."],["div",{"id":"27","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/7.27","order":"02.11.007.22786"},["b","27"],"For thou, O",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"of hosts, God of Israel, hast revealed to thy servant, saying, I will build thee an house: therefore hath thy servant found in his heart to pray this prayer unto thee."],["div",{"id":"28","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/7.28","order":"02.11.007.22787"},["b","28"],"And now, O Lord",["span.smallCaps","God"],", thou",["i","art"],"that God, and thy words be",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_28a"},"true"],", and thou hast promised this goodness unto thy servant:"],["div",{"id":"29","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/7.29","order":"02.11.007.22788"},["b","29"],"Therefore now let it please thee to bless the house of thy servant, that it may continue for ever before thee: for thou, O Lord",["span.smallCaps","God"],", hast spoken",["i","it:"],"and with thy blessing let the house of thy servant be blessed for ever."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/7.1a","order":"02.11.007.22789"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/7.11"},"2 Sam. 7:11"],"."],["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/7.2a","order":"02.11.007.22791"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/11.11"},"2 Sam. 11:11"],"."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/7.3a","order":"02.11.007.22793"},["b","3a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-chr/22.7"},"1 Chr. 22:7"],"."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/7.4a","order":"02.11.007.22795"},["b","4a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/12.1"},"2 Sam. 12:1"],"."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/7.5a","order":"02.11.007.22797"},["b","5a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/temple"},"TG Temple"],"."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/7.7a","order":"02.11.007.22799"},["b","7a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-chr/17.6"},"1 Chr. 17:6"],"."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/7.8a","order":"02.11.007.22801"},["b","8a"],["span.small","IE"],"sheepfold."],["div",{"id":"11a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/7.11a","order":"02.11.007.22803"},["b","11a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/judg/2.16.14-16"},"Judg. 2:16 (14–16)"],"."],["div",{"id":"11b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/7.11b","order":"02.11.007.22805"},["b","11b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/7.1"},"2 Sam. 7:1"],"."],["div",{"id":"11c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/7.11c","order":"02.11.007.22807"},["b","11c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ex/1.21.15-22"},"Ex. 1:21 (15–22)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/2.35.35-36"},"1 Sam. 2:35 (35–36)"],"."],["div",{"id":"12a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/7.12a","order":"02.11.007.22809"},["b","12a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/2.4"},"1 Kgs. 2:4"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/8.19.19-20"},"8:19 (19–20)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/2-chr/23.3"},"2 Chr. 23:3"],"."],["div",{"id":"13a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/7.13a","order":"02.11.007.22811"},["b","13a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/6.12"},"1 Kgs. 6:12"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/8.13"},"8:13"],"."],["div",{"id":"13b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/7.13b","order":"02.11.007.22813"},["b","13b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-davidic-descent-of"},"TG Jesus Christ, Davidic Descent of"],"."],["div",{"id":"14a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/7.14a","order":"02.11.007.22815"},["b","14a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/heb/1.5"},"Heb. 1:5"],"."],["div",{"id":"14b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/7.14b","order":"02.11.007.22817"},["b","14b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/5.7"},"Mosiah 5:7"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/27.25.24-26"},"27:25 (24–26)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/pgp/moses/6.68.64-68"},"Moses 6:68 (64–68)"],"."],["div",{"id":"14c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/7.14c","order":"02.11.007.22819"},["b","14c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/89.32.30-33"},"Ps. 89:32 (30–33)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/95.1.1-2"},"D&C 95:1 (1–2)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/101.4.4-5"},"101:4 (4–5)"],"."],["div",{"id":"16a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/7.16a","order":"02.11.007.22821"},["b","16a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/8.19.18-19"},"2 Kgs. 8:19 (18–19)"],"."],["div",{"id":"16b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/7.16b","order":"02.11.007.22823"},["b","16b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/9.5"},"1 Kgs. 9:5"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/luke/1.33"},"Luke 1:33"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/john/12.34"},"John 12:34"],"."],["div",{"id":"20a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/7.20a","order":"02.11.007.22825"},["b","20a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/139.1.1-4"},"Ps. 139:1 (1–4)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/morm/6.22"},"Morm. 6:22"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/6.16"},"D&C 6:16"],"."],["div",{"id":"21a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/7.21a","order":"02.11.007.22827"},["b","21a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-chr/17.19"},"1 Chr. 17:19"],"."],["div",{"id":"22a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/7.22a","order":"02.11.007.22829"},["b","22a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ex/8.10.8-10"},"Ex. 8:10 (8–10)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ex/15.11"},"15:11"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/8.23"},"1 Kgs. 8:23"],"."],["div",{"id":"23a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/7.23a","order":"02.11.007.22831"},["b","23a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/deut/4.7"},"Deut. 4:7"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/3.8"},"1 Kgs. 3:8"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/29.8"},"2 Ne. 29:8"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/9.20"},"Alma 9:20"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/pgp/abr/2.9"},"Abr. 2:9"],"."],["div",{"id":"24a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/7.24a","order":"02.11.007.22833"},["b","24a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/jacob/6.4"},"Jacob 6:4"],"."],["div",{"id":"24b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/7.24b","order":"02.11.007.22835"},["b","24b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/38.33"},"D&C 38:33"],"."],["div",{"id":"25a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/7.25a","order":"02.11.007.22837"},["b","25a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/119.38"},"Ps. 119:38"],"."],["div",{"id":"28a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/7.28a","order":"02.11.007.22839"},["b","28a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/john/17.17"},"John 17:17"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/31.15"},"2 Ne. 31:15"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/38.9"},"Alma 38:9"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/ether/4.12"},"Ether 4:12"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/20.11"},"D&C 20:11"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/66.11"},"66:11"],"."]]}
